  "text": "Moreover, it enables the separation of targeted dyes signal from intrinsic tissue AF, provided their lifetimes differ sufficiently [CITATION_1] . FLI can therefore provide enhanced sensitivity and contrast while allowing for lifetime-multiplexed detection using dyes with distinct lifetimes.",
